text:
RT @netshrink: Prevention is the best treatment.

1. Masks -cover your nose
2. Physical distancing avoid mass gatherings
3. Avoid closed sp‚Ä¶
retweet_text:
Prevention is the best treatment.

1. Masks -cover your nose
2. Physical distancing avoid mass gatherings
3. Avoid closed spaces eg. Clubs/restaurants/cinemas
4. Avoid travel unless essential & unavoidable
5. Take the vaccine if you are eligible. 

#COVID19India 
#SecondWave

text:

One day
the apolitical

small and alone.

text: RT @udaychopra: Depression, Anxiety, Social withdrawal, behavioral changes, over-indulgence in food, alcohol, drugs etc these are all signs‚Ä¶
retweet_text: Depression, Anxiety, Social withdrawal, behavioral changes, over-indulgence in food, alcohol, drugs etc these are all signs. If they continue for a longer period of time then there could be an issue. Most importantly do not judge them for it, instead try and understand them.

name: Vernika Awal
text:
RT @udaychopra: If you or a loved one is suffering from a mental illness get help.
Remember you cannot will it away. You cannot just ‚Äúthink‚Ä¶
retweet_text:
If you or a loved one is suffering from a mental illness get help.
Remember you cannot will it away. You cannot just ‚Äúthink positive‚Äù or ‚Äúshake it off‚Äù or ‚Äúbe strong‚Äù
It‚Äôs the same as asking a person with a broken leg to just walk it off
There is no shame in it; help is available

name: Vernika Awal
text: @MDIMADUD Aah, then you know that these patients are supremely intelligent as the condition doesn‚Äôt effect their IQ. He is playing it smart right now but is a threat to the life of others around him. We‚Äôve arranged for a pick up. Praying for the best. üôèüèº

name: Vernika Awal
text: Lastly, read up more on mental health. If not put to practical use, at least you‚Äôd end up gaining some more insight & it‚Äôs never to late to learn. Different mental health issues require different treatment - NOT EVERY ISSUE IS DEPRESSION.
location: Place(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x00000249D95B0548>, id='7a27222d4f7c432a', url='https://api.twitter.com/1.1/geo/id/7a27222d4f7c432a.json', place_type='city', name='Jalandhar', full_name='Jalandhar, India', country_code='IN', country='India', contained_within=[], bounding_box=BoundingBox(_api=<tweepy.api.API object at 0x00000249D95B0548>, type='Polygon', coordinates=[[[75.441473, 31.206242], [75.822406, 31.206242], [75.822406, 31.61479], [75.441473, 31.61479]]]), attributes={})

name: Vernika Awal
text: We‚Äôve lost gems to depression & psychiatric issues, which could be treated. What drives people to extremes is loneliness, remember that. Every person you meet is a potential victim & only in need of your time. Please be more genuine. üôèüèº

name: Vernika Awal
text: Please don‚Äôt just put out messages of ‚ÄúI am there for you,‚Äù in the wake of a tragic step taken by a popular & venerable person. Say this, only when you mean it. Understand the gravity & impact of your words. Always remember, today it is someone else, tomorrow it can be you.

name: Vernika Awal
text: It has taken us almost 24 hours & zero help from any certified authority to arrange for the safety of our patient & people around him. To live in a society where even while being surrounded with thousands, you find yourself alone. This is what drives people to extremes.

name: Vernika Awal
text: Through personal experience I can say that whatever we say, this country is not prepared to handle mental stigmas. Hospitals that do not cooperate, people who qualify mental health as ‚Äúpaagalpan‚Äù and the society who is too quick to judge.  #MentalHealth

name: Vernika Awal
text:
RT @SharmaAnshika: And most importantly, please stop saying, ‚Äúwhy didn‚Äôt you tell me?‚Äù ‚ÄúWhy didn‚Äôt did they talk to us?‚Äù
If you want to hel‚Ä¶
retweet_text:
And most importantly, please stop saying, ‚Äúwhy didn‚Äôt you tell me?‚Äù ‚ÄúWhy didn‚Äôt did they talk to us?‚Äù
If you want to help, look at what YOU can do, instead of what a person we‚Äôve already established is struggling can do.
#MentalHealthMatters #anthonybordain #RIPKateSpade

name: Vernika Awal
text: RT @SharmaAnshika: Instead, be more observant. If you see someone who you feel needs to talk, just ask! Be kinder. Make a safe space. Not e‚Ä¶
retweet_text: Instead, be more observant. If you see someone who you feel needs to talk, just ask! Be kinder. Make a safe space. Not everyone has been taught how to ask for help & not all mental health issues work the same way. Don‚Äôt tell someone in emotional agony how to be in emotional agony

name: Vernika Awal
text: RT @SharmaAnshika: As great as place as the ‚Äòask for help‚Äô well-meaning advice comes from, it can be counterproductive. There‚Äôs stigma and‚Ä¶
retweet_text: As great as place as the ‚Äòask for help‚Äô well-meaning advice comes from, it can be counterproductive. There‚Äôs stigma and there‚Äôs a lot struggle. It‚Äôs hard to accept the extent of your mental health issues, sometimes, let alone being able to speak about them to someone.
